{"tid":2079194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文分析] 其實有無人知，美國大選你睇民調其實係無意思","createTime":"2020-06-25T15:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T14:16:46.000Z","uid":52658,"like":29,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d67b22a5b1def6862a7b6df77ed4cb2bf195f482","tid":2079194,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:29:09.000Z","msg":"有無人知 其實美國大選唔係睇整體民調<br />\n而係睇六大搖擺州份既民調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為美國既選舉人票制度<br />\n多數州份一定係共和黨或者民主黨其中一邊既地頭<br />\n好似德州一定係深紅 加州一定係深藍 <br />\n呢個定律黎唔會變<br />\n真正決勝負既係呢幾個搖擺州<br />\n所以淨係睇呢d搖擺州既民調就得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假設基本盤無變 如果拜登係加州贏兩千萬票<br />\n川普係佛州 賓州同威斯康星州贏兩票<br />\n結果都會係川普贏<br />\n所以你睇民調會發現<br />\n拜登head成十幾趴就係咁解<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bK2AVny.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbK2AVny.png&h=63b4917c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然睇個勢 川普都唔樂觀<br />\n但未至於輸硬<br />\n仲有四個幾月咁多 咩都有可能發生<br />\n仲有個辯論會<br />\n當初蔡英文都係咁上下時間開始追過韓國瑜<br />\n四個月內 川普只要係呢六個州入面執到三個<br />\n咁就會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申無票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n情感上想川普贏 <br />\n理智上就支持拜登"},{"pid":"05d79bd8964057f15ece09f1f9952698c9222ec0","tid":2079194,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:35:23.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認真post無人理"},{"pid":"78cc33ca6ba845111bec06d5590d11f142598a7b","tid":2079194,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"05d79bd8964057f15ece09f1f9952698c9222ec0","tid":2079194,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:35:23.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認真post無人理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:36:34.000Z","msg":"無架啦呢個時間"},{"pid":"2589738ff7a96d82192dc096c8a16f72043a184b","tid":2079194,"uid":52658,"like":0,"disli