贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8668dd7c3d26581f5e36b1cda7be7f4ebdfa8e59","tid":2079194,"uid":37722,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:48:58.000Z","msg":"想知點解理智上會支持china jor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd077677b51dbdf328292afde6ff9662a15a03e","tid":2079194,"uid":52658,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ebd26136f0c367c79042288040f158ea554eab99","tid":2079194,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:43:31.000Z","msg":"Ohio點<br />\n好似話1960年之後冇總統係輸Ohio 而最後贏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:50:31.000Z","msg":"我覺得俄亥俄同搖擺賓州會輸<br />\n但如果民主黨係呢幾個月有咩出包 <br />\n或者川普搞得掂武肺 佛州同威斯康星會贏<br />\n淨返果d就睇共和黨好唔好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0598cbc35ac6873726c57352ff7b63f4bda66c57","tid":2079194,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:54:41.000Z","msg":"近年民調同媒體都係親左派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>[⇩ 港獨強心針 ⇩]</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/pAcortX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/pAcortX</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"01beb33c641c5b19aa330605372bf732bca6726d","tid":2079194,"uid":52658,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"8668dd7c3d26581f5e36b1cda7be7f4ebdfa8e59","tid":2079194,"uid":37722,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:48:58.000Z","msg":"想知點解理智上會支持china jor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:55:37.000Z","msg":"因川普係疫情同示威方面真係做得好差<br />\n加上川普再做落去既<br />\n會更加將歐盟同日本南韓推向中國<br />\n<br />\n雖然拜登有親中前科<br />\n但而家暫時黎睇 拜登把口係幾硬<br />\n同埋民主黨一旦上台既 會更加focas係經濟民生方面<br />\n而家反中係兩黨共識 <br />\n所以即使拜登上左台 我唔覺得佢會有能力令美國既國策改變"},{